
LargeMatrix Class
================================
Library dependencies:
	C++ Standard library, std==c++0x
	Boost Filesystem & System, version 1.50
	libgsl, libgslcblas (part of libgsl), and libm, for generating random numbers
	libconfig++, library for creating configuration files


All parts of this module live in namespace Mtx

Class:
	Member Function --
		Description


LargeMatrix:
	ctor LargeMatrix(string filename, enum iostate, int num_in_memory)
		Creates a LargeMatrix object by specifying the location of a file and declaring how many numbers to store in memory at a time.

	static int EstimateMaxSize(int num_rows)
		Returns the max size (in MB) of a matrix with the given number of rows
	static void GenerateRandom(string filename, int num_rows)
		Generates a random matrix of the given size, primarily for testing

